      {#AlertH2Format}Bug Fixes{#Prev}
      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack Fixed issues preventing {#AlertBoldFormat}Gorgon Amulet (Athena) {#Prev}from activating on {#AlertBoldFormat}Mount Olympus
      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack Fixed cases where {#AlertBoldFormat}Hermes {#Prev}Boons would not start appearing when expected on newer save files
