      · Fixed {#AlertBoldFormat}Slow Cooker (Hestia) {#Prev}adding Power to more than Attacks and Specials, contrary to the description
      · Fixed {#AlertBoldFormat}Acceptance of Another Fate {#Prev}not re-randomizing the effects of certain Keepsakes
      · Fixed {#AlertBoldFormat}Trusty Shield (Hephaestus) {#Prev}removing Armor if it later gained Rarity
      · Fixed cases where both {#AlertBoldFormat}Artemis {#Prev}and {#AlertBoldFormat}Athena {#Prev}could appear in the same Encounter {#AlertItalicFormat}(they work alone)
      · Fixed {#AlertBoldFormat}Engraved Pin (Moros) {#Prev}sometimes not deactivating the effect of {#AlertBoldFormat}Strength (Arcana) {#Prev}as expected
      · Fixed {#AlertBoldFormat}Raki {#Prev}leaving all the work to you in {#AlertBoldFormat}Oceanus {#Prev}exit-unsealing Encounters 
      · Fixed the {#AlertBoldFormat}Chronos {#Prev}entry in the {#AlertBoldFormat}Book of Shadows {#Prev}not always appearing as expected 
      · Fixed cases of {#AlertBoldFormat}Odysseus {#Prev}incorrectly identifying recently harvested Plants
      · Fixed visual issue where the {#AlertBoldFormat}Snow Queen (Demeter) {#Prev}shield did not move with Melinoë in some cases
      · Many other minor fixes

