      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack You now can see your {#AlertBoldFormat}Change of Fate {#Prev}count when choosing Boons
      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack You now can exchange resources for {#AlertBoldFormat}Prestige {#Prev}more freely, with a new warning if you still need them
      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack The {#AlertBoldFormat}Victory Screen {#Prev}now has theming differences depending on which route you cleared
      · Improved feedback in the {#AlertBoldFormat}Altar of Ashes {#Prev}for when you fully upgrade your {#AlertBoldFormat}Grasp
      · Improved presentation when multiple Incantations are revealed at once in the {#AlertBoldFormat}Crossroads Cauldron
      · Improved text descriptions for {#AlertBoldFormat}Animal Familiar {#Prev}upgrades
