      {#AlertH2Format}Music & SFX{#Prev}
      · Added new music pieces for the final confrontation and the lead-up to it
      · Added music theme for {#AlertBoldFormat}Icarus
      · Added music theme for {#AlertBoldFormat}Echo
      · Added a song from {#Spoiler}Artemis
      · Added unlockable versions of each of these to the {#AlertBoldFormat}Music Maker
