      {#AlertH2Format}Daedalus Hammer Upgrades{#Prev}
      @GUI\\Icons\\GhostPack {#AlertHighlightFormat}Executioner's Chop (Axe){#Prev}: no longer prevents you from striking if you have insufficient Magick
