      {#AlertH2Format}Path of Stars{#Prev}
      · {#AlertHighlightFormat}Growth (Dark Side){#Prev}: {#AlertBoldFormat}new! {#Prev}Makes your Hex passively recharge over time
      · {#AlertHighlightFormat}Preparation (Total Eclipse){#Prev}: {#AlertBoldFormat}new! {#Prev}Start Encounters with your Hex partially charged
      · {#AlertHighlightFormat}Extinction (Twilight Curse){#Prev}: reduced effectiveness
